<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LinkedOUT: are you fr??</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('common/header') %>
    
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 4rem;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">LinkedOUT: are you fr??</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            A game where you attempt to guess whether a LinkedIn post is fake or genuinely batshit insane.
        </p>
        
        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            <a href="/game" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size: 1.2rem; padding: 1rem 2.5rem;">Play Game Now!</a>
        </div>

        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline">Login</a>
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-outline">Register</a>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="display: inline-block; padding: 1rem;">
            <img src="/linkedOUT.png" alt="LinkedOUT Logo" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: var(--radius);">
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('common/footer') %>
</body>
</html>